    <h2>BMW 3 Series Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Engine: Inline 4 Turbo</li>
      <li>Horsepower: 255 hp</li>
      <li>Price: $42,000</li>
      <li>Fuel Efficiency: 26 city / 36 highway MPG</li>
      <li>Available in sedan and sports variants</li>
      <li>Standard 8-speed automatic transmission</li>
      <li>Advanced driver assistance features (lane keep assist, adaptive cruise control)</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>BMW X5 Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Engine: 3.0L I6 Turbocharged</li>
    <li>Horsepower: 335 hp</li>
    <li>Price: $60,000</li>
    <li>Fuel Efficiency: 21 city / 27 highway MPG</li>
    <li>All-Wheel Drive (AWD) for superior handling</li>
    <li>Optional third-row seating</li>
    <li>Large touchscreen with BMW iDrive 7.0 system</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>BMW M4 Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Engine: 3.0L Inline 6 Turbocharged</li>
    <li>Horsepower: 473 hp</li>
    <li>Price: $72,000</li>
    <li>Fuel Efficiency: 16 city / 23 highway MPG</li>
    <li>0-60 mph: 3.8 seconds</li>
    <li>Rear-wheel drive with high-performance suspension</li>
    <li>Active M Differential for optimal handling and traction</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>BMW i4 Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Engine: Electric Motor (335 hp)</li>
    <li>Price: $55,000</li>
    <li>Range: Up to 300 miles on a full charge</li>
    <li>Fast-charging: 80% charge in less than 40 minutes</li>
    <li>Zero emissions and eco-friendly interior options</li>
    <li>Integrated navigation and real-time traffic updates</li>
    <li>Advanced driver assistance features, including collision warning and automatic braking</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>BMW 7 Series Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Engine: 4.4L V8 Turbocharged</li>
    <li>Horsepower: 523 hp</li>
    <li>Price: $95,000</li>
    <li>Fuel Efficiency: 18 city / 25 highway MPG</li>
    <li>Luxury interior with premium leather seating and wood trim</li>
    <li>Massaging and heated seats for ultimate comfort</li>
    <li>BMW's Gesture Control technology for easy interaction with the infotainment system</li>
  </ul>
